---
description: Release and production-gate rules.
globs:
  - "approvals/**"
  - ".github/workflows/**"
  - "infra/terraform/environments/production/**"
  - "docs/execution/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Release

- Do: require named human approvals for production.
- Do: keep `make production-preflight` validation-only (no deploy).
- Do: mark legal/policy drafts as UNAPPROVED until counsel signs.
- Never: disable branch protection, secret scanning, or release signing.
- Never: fabricate audit, legal, or approval artifacts.
- Verify: production gate exits non-zero without authentic approvals.
